purpose:
(Clinical Focus: This set of values contains codes for laboratory test names associated with detecting the nucleic acid of non-specific organisms from a normally sterile site),(Data Element Scope: Laboratory tests names that were ordered or observed.),(Inclusion Criteria: VSAC query: Nucleic Acid Sterile Site;
LOINC Search: "(microorganism or pathogens) (blood or serum or plasma or cerebral or CSF or tissue or fluid) nucleic acid -panel"),(Exclusion Criteria: Exclude LOINC codes for the following Systems: (Anal, Cervix, Genital, Genital fld, Genital mucus, Pus, Throat, Urethra, Urine, Vag, Bronchial, Ear, Nose, Sputum, Stool, Semen, Wound).
Exclude panel tests.)
